{"tid":722891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國足球隊回國記招被掟雞蛋，孫興慜中招","createTime":"2018-06-30T02:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T11:37:30.000Z","uid":103207,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2a47315c03a4a89e75ba3a39460824aedad67bc7","tid":722891,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"[影片] 壓力真大！打敗世界冠軍還不夠，韓國隊返國記者會被砸雞蛋，孫興慜中招一臉錯愕<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;By&nbsp;維克特<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;2018-06-30<br />\n<br />\n結束了俄羅斯世界盃之旅的韓國隊昨天返回國門，雖然韓國隊沒有成功晉級，但能在世界盃擊敗世界冠軍德國，這結果應該還是值得讚許的，但沒想到在機場舉行的記者會上，居然有球迷向他們扔雞蛋。網友們對此紛紛表示：韓國球迷要求這麼高？還要怎樣！？<br />\n<br />\n6月29日下午，結束世界盃的韓國從俄羅斯搭機回國，仁川機場為韓國隊設立了媒體見面會專區，據了解現場來了500名記者和球迷。<br />\n<br />\n韓國隊本屆世界盃上1勝2負排在小組第三，不過他們最後一場比賽2比0擊敗世界盃衛冕冠軍德國隊，很多韓國球迷為國家隊的驚人表現讚歎不已。<br />\n<br />\n但未能完成小組賽出線的任務，總教練申臺龍還是向現場球迷鞠躬表示歉意，「我本來期待7月份回來，可是現在6月就回來了。」<br />\n<br />\n他也帶領韓國全隊也向現場所有人鞠躬致歉，不過隨後，韓國足協主席鄭夢奎準備發言時，現場突然飛出來一個雞蛋，所有球員都嚇了一跳。隨後更有球迷把枕頭扔到國腳們面前，工作人員迅速拿出雨傘，防止意外再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n隨後是頭號球星、在對德國隊比賽中進球的孫興慜代表球員發言，沒想到突然又一個雞蛋扔了進來，砸到了孫興慜腳附近，弄得他有些不知所措。不過大部分球迷還是相當理智，現場大多數人紛紛指責扔雞蛋的球迷，希望他們趕緊住手。<br />\n<br />\n只能說韓國人對國家隊真的要求很高，或許他們的目標就是至少16強，所以對最終結果相當不滿意，身為球員真的有相當大的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dongtw.com/2018-fifa-world-cup/20180630/863959.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dongtw.com%2F2018-fifa-world-cup%2F20180630%2F863959.html&d=xYDnsYMJANfNLmNsctYieYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=658a6ae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dongtw.com/2018-fifa-world-cup/20180630/863959.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898a8e22c5a75069050e169be087922879cf275f","tid":722891,"uid":42820,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d6/Tsangwordp1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20071130025148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd6%2FTsangwordp1.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071130025148&h=30e6be5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e5ea54ce8b9691a2669969213c1d186c0ca4baa","tid":722891,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"係最後一場拎返個尾彩，頭兩場咪又係成碌柒咁"},{"pid":"05ead01631e643cc0da4919739fa758cfbae63fa","tid":722891,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"主要係日本晉級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8eec91b886d3abf635101392c804e6feb9033a9","tid":722891,"uid":57504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"廢閪泡菜，淨係識格鬥掟蛋紅外線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47ec9a0ecdb9f980542908705a2f9ed4ee05d24","tid":722891,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15302727579695d45cb4451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F15302727579695d45cb4451&h=ac9eead4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15302727581471b00995dbc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F15302727581471b00995dbc&h=e99f4006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1530272758238bebb45ade7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F1530272758238bebb45ade7&h=931bd2c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1530272758337e1fd2dc78f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image